{"tid":1786261,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕經典《Last Christmas》MV 官方Remastered 推出 4K畫質版本","createTime":"2019-12-17T04:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T08:18:51.000Z","uid":79562,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4c81e15bfb09c7d7b61a4b5a75943cf2c454df","tid":1786261,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:16:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bwNV7TAWN3M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbwNV7TAWN3M&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0j%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=400e32ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bwNV7TAWN3M</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1217-5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1217-5a.jpg&h=363ea63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有些歌曲每逢聖誕臨近都會在電台節目，甚至商場或餐廳聽得到，Wham! 的經典「Last Christmas」就是其中之一。這首歌在 1984 年 12 月 20 日發行，至今已經 35 年，就算你是 90 後，這首聖誕歌都肯定在不同渠道聽過。<br />\n<br />\n最近 Sony Music Entertainment 決定將「Last Christmas」的 MV 原裝片段，Remastered 成為 4K 並上載到 YouTube。經典金曲本身沒有因為 Remastered 而有任何改變，但 80 年代拍攝的 MV 看起來就有怪怪的感覺。Wham! 的 80 年代誇張髮型、化妝和衣飾在 4K 高清畫面中出現，就好像是唱片公司刻意在 2019 年翻拍一樣，還是配上鬆郁矇的感覺比較合襯。<br />\n<br />\n為了讓這首經典聖誕金曲能夠延續下去，Sony Music 將 MV 高清化得相當徹底，不得不讚賞他們的誠意。<br />\n<br />\n來源：theverge"},{"pid":"72a207e3a0765ff7f9bcf1b66cef58873f06ea3f","tid":1786261,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"622ccb4ba161281125f951ef39da48429a23ab76","tid":1786261,"uid":49144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"George Micheal"},{"pid":"3c96e68620b51f33ad97e41b539866527df8964c","tid":1786261,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:59:15.000Z","msg":"you said you were gay"},{"pid":"ed6a18d61a953ddbeeac3df1f2fbfdccf248483d","tid":1786261,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit